## HOW TO UPDATE STATUS
After completing each step, update the checklist above by changing [ ] to [x].
This keeps Cursor oriented even in long sessions.

## CHANGELOG POLICY
- Keep `CHANGELOG.md` up to date for every completed step and meaningful feature change.
- Add entries under `## Unreleased` grouped by category (`Added`, `Changed`, `Fixed`, `Removed`).
- Update the changelog in the same change set where implementation is done; never postpone it.
